value.0: Stoic, poised, and dedicated, the masked Temple Guards of the Jedi Order are a well-honored sect of anonymous warriors sworn to defend Jedi temples with their lives.

Guests to the temple and its grounds must keep their weapons stowed unless given leave by a Jedi Knight.

Guests are welcome, but are expected to be respectful and not to interrupt ongoing lessons.

Do not disturb the Temple Guards from their duties.

Non-Jedi must be accompanied by at least one Jedi of Padawan or higher standing to enter the Temple interior.

Those seeking knowledge of the Order to join its ranks should speak to any active member.
